INGREDIENTS LIST:

Thai Green Chicken Curry (57%), Cooked Jasmine Rice (43%).

Thai Green Chicken Curry contains: Water, Cooked Australian RSPCA Approved Chicken (17%), Coconut Cream (11%) [Coconut Cream, Stabilisers (415, 412, 407)], Onion, White Sugar, Green Curry Paste (3.5%), Fish Sauce, Corn Starch, Canola Oil, Lemon Juice from Concentrate, Salt.

Cooked Jasmine Rice contains: Jasmine Rice, Canola Oil, Salt.
